    {
      "text": "26\n3\n\nSo here I’ve been for six and a half years going around with the conviction that by the way I handled the Xerox missive I performed what I call \"the heroic act\" that introduced newness \"and overcame my karma\"; by \"karma\" read programming. Well, I am right. What I did, by not answering the Xerox missive, did change my life. There is no telling what PKD2 (Thomas) would have done if he had been able to go ahead and answer the Xerox missive. \"An intelligence officer in the Army,\" as the AI voi",
